(Please note: A baggie of pumpkin shaped glitters in orange and black will be included with this polish - to add to your nail, as you see fit.) *** The Haunting Hour - Various sized hex and square glitters in a mix of black, gun metal, orange and silver holo, including silver holo moons and stars, sprinkled with micro holo glitter in a clear base. *** Corn Maze - Various sized hex and square glitters in shades of gold, yellows, holo gold, and browns, sprinkled with micro holo glitter in a clear base. *** Frank N. name: The Mouse Collection
description: Visit my facebook page for more pictures of each color and blogger reviews. *** M-I-C-K-E-Y - mouse shaped silver holo glitters, mixed with various sized hex glitters in red, black, white, and yellow, sprinkled with micro holo glitter in a clear base. *** Pop Art Mickey - mouse shaped silver holo glitters, mixed with neon pink and neon green stars, and various sized hex glitters in neon pink, neon green, neon blue and red, sprinkled with micro holo glitter in a clear base. *** Mousetasia - mouse shaped silver holo glitters, mixed with various sized hex glitters in red, blue, and silver, holo silver stars and moons, sprinkled with micro holo glitter in a dark blue jelly base. *** Minnie’s Tulips - mouse shaped silver holo glitters, mixed with various sized hex glitters in pink holo and rose copper, sprinkled with micro holo glitter in a clear base. *** Minnie’s Bouquet - mouse shaped silver holo glitters, mixed with a various ‘bouquet’ of girly shapes – flowers, butterflies, hearts, and stars, along with various sized hex, square, micro bar glitters in a mix of purple and silver shades – matte, metallic, and even iridescent glitters, sprinkled with micro holo glitter in a clear base. *** Minnie’s Party Dress - mouse shaped silver holo glitters, mixed with white dots and micro holo glitter in a hot pink jelly base. Special thanks to Adventures In Acetone for her awesome nail art pics! :)

name: Minions In A Bottle
description: Visit my facebook page for more pictures of each color and blogger reviews. The name says it all! Minions In A Bottle - those fun loving yellow guys all bottled up! A mix of blue, yellow, and black hex glitters, white and silver holo circle glitters, and micro holo glitter! You will 'Beep-Beep-Bo-Beep' the day away with this fun polish on your nails! :)

name: Elvis Has Left The Building
description: Visit my facebook page for more pictures of each color and blogger reviews. A special polish made in memory of Elvis and one of his famous jumpsuits! A white jelly based polish, with red, blue, and gold glitters in various sizes and holo gold stars! Long live the King!!! Check out swatches and review from Dressed Up Digits here - Link You will surely be a 'Hunka, hunka burning love' with this polish on your nails! ;)

name: Aloha From Hawaii <3 Elvis
description: Visit my facebook page for more pictures of each color and blogger reviews. Another polish in memory of Elvis! The King was known for giving away Lei's at his Hawaii concert - here we have all that combined into a bottle! Flower glitters in five different colors - combined with various sized 'ocean' colored glitters and micro fine holo and teal glitter. It's like having the big island, right on your nails! :) Check out swatches/review from Dressed Up Digits here - Link

name: Ball Pit
description: Visit my facebook page for more pictures of each color and blogger reviews. Ball Pit - a wonderful glitter top coat filled to the brim with various sizes and colors of circle 'ball' glitters! Including micro fine holo glitters - to give it that extra sparkle! Who doesn't love jumping into the Ball Pit?!?!?! Spread the fun on your nails! Check out the review of Ball Pit by My Nail Polish Obsession here: Link Check out MNPO Instagram video of the sparkle from Ball Pit! Video

name: Kick A$$
description: Visit my facebook page for more pictures of each color and blogger reviews. A magenta based polish filled to the brim with tiny magenta holo glitters and a slight blue shimmer. You will be amazed at the color and sparkle of this polish! It's Kick A$$!!! ;) Check out a review by MNPO here - Link She also posted an another awesome sparkly video on Instagram! Check it here: Video Check out the review from Dressed Up Digits here - Link Thank you to both ladies for beautiful swatches! :)

name: Once You Go Black...
description: Visit my facebook page for more pictures of each color and blogger reviews. This polish is inspired by Sirius Black from the Harry Potter series. :) A black jelly based polish with loads of micro fine black holo glitters and a purple shimmer. This one is a stunner - like a galaxy on your nails! Check out My Nail Polish Obsession's review here: Once You Go Black... She even posted a short video of the sparkly goodness! Check it out: Video

name: The Original Series Collection
description: Visit my facebook page for more pictures of each color and blogger reviews. ● “The Captain” – gold in color and bold and daring! No female shall resist! I. believe. we. have. an. excellent. leader. here! ● “The Engineer” – red in color and on the alert! Never will there be ‘not enough power’ with this polish! Don’t worry though, it will always leave it’s phasers on ‘stun’! ● “The Doctor” – blue is the color here to heal all your wounds and suffering! Precise and knowledgeable – this polish will always be sure to please. (Please note – “I’m a polish, not a doctor!” – haha) ● “The Temptress” – green is the color of her skin – but she still is lovely and seductive! The more you see of her – the more she shall lull you into her alluring shimmer and shine – till you shall no longer be able to resist!
